====選手變動====
* [[青山博一|青山博一]]在2012年瓦倫西亞站後，全職回到MotoGP。<ref name=EntryList/> He will ride an [[FTR_Moto|FTR Moto]] prepared by [[Avintia_Racing|Avintia Racing]].
* [[Héctor_Barberá|Héctor Barberá]]在2012賽季後，離開了[[Pramac_Racing|Pramac Racing]]。後加入了CRT的Avintia Blusens車隊中。<ref>{{cite news|title=Hector Barbera planning CRT MotoGP move|url=http://www.crash.net/motogp/news/183902/1/hector_barbera_planning_crt_motogp_move.html|work=Crash.net|publisher=Crash Media Group|date=13 September 2012|accessdate=14 September 2012|archive-date=2013-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130626121136/http://www.crash.net/motogp/news/183902/1/hector_barbera_planning_crt_motogp_move.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* [[Claudio_Corti_(motorcycle_racer)|Claudio Corti]]進入MotoGP，加入[[Colin_Edwards|Colin Edwards]]所在的[[Forward_Racing|Forward Racing]]車隊中。<ref name=EntryList/>
* [[Andrea_Dovizioso|Andrea Dovizioso]]原本在[[Monster_Yamaha_Tech_3|Monster Yamaha Tech 3]]，在2012年賽季結束後，取代了[[瓦伦蒂诺·罗西|瓦倫蒂諾·羅西]]在[[Ducati_Corse|杜卡迪]]的位置。<ref name="Dovi Ducati"/>
* [[瓦伦蒂诺·罗西|瓦倫蒂諾·羅西]]在[[Ducati_Corse|Ducati]]待了兩年的賽季後，回到了[[Yamaha_Motor_Racing|山葉]].<ref name="Rossi">{{cite news|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/101761|title=Valentino Rossi returns to Yamaha for 2013 MotoGP season|work=Autosport|date=10 August 2012|accessdate=10 August 2012|archive-date=2016-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160807140656/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/101761|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* [[Yonny_Hernández|Yonny Hernández]]從[[Avintia_Racing|Avintia Racing]]車隊換到[[Paul_Bird_Motorsport|Paul Bird Motorsport]]車隊。<ref name=EntryList/>
* [[Michael_Laverty|Michael Laverty]]結束了其2010到2012的[[英國超級摩托車大賽|英國超級摩托車大賽]]，加入了MotoGP的[[Paul_Bird_Motorsport|Paul Bird Motorsport]]車隊。<ref name=EntryList/>
* [[Andrea_Iannone|Andrea Iannone]]在2013年開始，從Moto2晉升至MotoGP加入了Pramac Racing。<ref name="Pramac"/>
* [[馬克·馬爾克斯|馬克·馬爾克斯]]進入MotoGP的[[Repsol_Honda|Repsol Honda Team]]。<ref name="Repsol"/>
* [[Bryan_Staring|Bryan Staring]]全職進入MotoGP CRT的[[Gresini_Racing|Gresini Racing]]車隊中。<ref name=EntryList/>
* [[Mattia_Pasini|Mattia Pasini]]在2013年回到了Moto2的[[Forward_Racing|Forward Racing]]車隊中。<ref name=EntryList/>
* [[James_Ellison_(motorcycle_racer)|James Ellison]]從[[Paul_Bird_Motorsport|Paul Bird Motorsport]]車隊選手中除名。<ref name=EntryList/>
* [[Michele_Pirro|Michele Pirro]]從[[Gresini_Racing|Gresini Racing]]車隊選手中除名。<ref name=EntryList/>
